short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension enables searching for domain information that is registered on address.services.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This extension provides an easy and quick way to check detailed information about domains related to the Address Services. Obtain relevant data, such as ownership and more, to enhance your online experience in the cryptodomains realm.

Key Features:

- Fast Query: Instantly verify information about any domain related to Address Services.
- Comprehensive Details: Uncover crucial data, including ownership.
